Package com.coreconsulting.res.openehr.tdd2rm.transformer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractTransformer
    This class abstracts the concept of a transformer that is capable of transforming a TDD element of a specific type, making it compliant to the openEHR Reference Model.
    ActionTransformer
    This class implements the transformation of an ACTION from the TDD so that it complies to the openEHR Reference Model.
    ActivityTransformer
    This class implements the transformation of an ACTIVITY from the TDD so that it complies to the openEHR Reference Model.
    AdminEntryTransformer
    This class implements the transformation of an ADMIN_ENTRY from the TDD so that it complies to the openEHR Reference Model.
    ClusterTransformer
    This class implements the transformation of a CLUSTER from the TDD so that it complies to the openEHR Reference Model.
    CompositionTransformer
    This class implements the transformation of a COMPOSITION from the TDD so that it complies to the openEHR Reference Model.
    ElementTransformer
    This class implements the transformation of an ELEMENT from the TDD so that it complies to the openEHR Reference Model.
    EvaluationTransformer
    This class implements the transformation of an EVALUATION from the TDD so that it complies to the openEHR Reference Model.
    InstructionTransformer
    This class implements the transformation of an INSTRUCTION from the TDD so that it complies to the openEHR Reference Model.
    IntervalEventTransformer
    This class implements the transformation of an INTERVAL_EVENT from the TDD so that it complies to the openEHR Reference Model.
    ItemTreeTransformer
    This class implements the transformation of an ITEM_TREE from the TDD so that it complies to the openEHR Reference Model.
    LocatableTransformer
    This class implements the transformation of a LOCATABLE from the TDD so that it complies to the openEHR Reference Model.
    ObservationTransformer
    This class implements the transformation of an OBSERVATION from the TDD so that it complies to the openEHR Reference Model.
    PointEventTransformer
    This class implements the transformation of a POINT_EVENT from the TDD so that it complies to the openEHR Reference Model.
    SectionTransformer
    This class implements the transformation of a SECTION from the TDD so that it complies to the openEHR Reference Model.
    TransformerFactory
    This class implements the functionality related to providing transformers for the TDD transformation.
